Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:10.64,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.86,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all for gathering here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:42.10,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us begin the \NRoyal Knights Selection Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:47.28,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Knights Selection Exam was \Nabout to be conducted in preparation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:49.48,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,for fighting the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:52.86,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Then a mysterious man suddenly \Nappeared at the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:52.86,sign_18145_218_Xerx_L__gner,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(174,1)\blur3}Xerx Lügner
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:52.86,sign_18128_215_Mimosa_Vermillio,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Mimosa Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:56.57,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad! I'm a little late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:00.39,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Xerx Lügner. It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:08.37,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta ended up on a team with this unknown \Nman, Xerx, for the exam tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:16.84,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, the Royal Knights Selection Exam \Nbegan amidst an ominous atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:19.93,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're about to begin round one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:28.23,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Are both teams ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:33.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting hyped!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:03.06,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(187,1)}Flower of Resolution
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:15.69,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! Kick some ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:18.50,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Show them what the Black Bulls are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.19,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:23.01,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and finish them \Noff so you can fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:28.02,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I know you can win before \NI even have a chance to blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:33.62,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of magic \Nwe'll see. I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:37.01,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La! Have a snack while you watch the event, la.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:38.03,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hyped!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:51.24,sign_23512_280_C_Team_Sol_Marro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(750,750)}B Team\NMimosa Vermillion   Asta   Xerx Lügner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.54,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:49.52,top,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so excited about? \NThis is an exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.24,top,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Take this seriously, you dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:55.88,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,We should be scouting the area and \Nthinking up strategies, you dumb shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:04:00.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you say something so right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:03.38,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I say is right, you shitty little shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.70,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, calm down, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.89,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's so cute, even when he's frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:15.28,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,As Xerx mentioned, we should learn each \Nother's abilities and figure out a strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:18.02,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the enemy team \Nwill be doing that, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You're right, Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:23.82,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I specialize in healing \Nand support plant magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:28.66,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta shines best in close-range combat \Nwith his magic-nullifying anti-magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:31.50,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of magic do you use, Xerx?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:38.13,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy team is attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:40.38,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This early? Where did it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:43.56,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, we need to guard the crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.26,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:50.35,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a long-distance attack... \NAnd yet they're hitting it perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How are they...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.61,top,Rick,0000,0000,0000,,Move three meters toward 10 o' clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:05:00.50,sign_7061_51_A_Team_Coral_Pea,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1023,910)}A Team\NThe Coral Peacocks 3rd Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Rick Cornell
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.75,italicstop,Forti,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.07,top,Rick,0000,0000,0000,,With my Crystal Magic: Crystal Scope,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:05.15,main,Rick,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell exactly where you're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.87,sign_7061_51_A_Team_Coral_Pea,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}A Team\NThe Crimson Lion Kings 4th Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Forti Griss
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.87,top,Forti,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you insult the Wizard King, you cur?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:12.12,sign_7061_51_A_Team_Coral_Pea,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}A Team\NThe Silver Eagles 3rd Class Senior Magic Knight \N{\fs30}Curtis Wolne
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:12.12,top,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,We refuse to give you a chance to shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:16.70,main,Forti,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Burst Javelin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.13,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Rock Magic: Strong Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! This is gonna be over in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We need to work together and—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:36.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:37.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hurgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.54,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, is he asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.51,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:41.53,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:42.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.46,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:46.66,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Being seen sleeping by so many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.99,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed just thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:55.22,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. Looks like we \Nhave some sleepyheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.89,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two not getting enough sleep? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:05:59.58,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you sleeping?! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:04.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to lose at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:06.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to all those \Nreasonable points you made?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:10.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:13.51,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care if I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:17.29,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how much you \Nwant to win, nor do I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:20.02,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Get off my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:22.91,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I was up all night. I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:26.18,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,And you can't work on no sleep, \Nso sleep comes first right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.63,main,rick,0000,0000,0000,,That Xerx guy is asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.87,italics,Forti,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's some kind of strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:37.20,main,Rick,0000,0000,0000,,No... My Crystal Scope can also \Ndetermine someone's physical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:40.75,main,Rick,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:46.28,main,Forti,0000,0000,0000,,First, he's rude to the Wizard King, \Nand now he's being this irresponsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.01,main,Forti,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:52.46,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what he might have up his sleeve,\N they cannot win without moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:54.53,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Let us end this here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:59.38,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Plant Creation Magic: Magic Flower Guidepost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.39,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Two of our enemies are near their crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:06.82,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,The other is about 60 meters \Nahead of them, up in a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.45,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,The two in back are building up mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.04,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're going to cast a combo spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.78,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,But from so far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:16.61,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:17.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.87,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That was a super fast attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:23.29,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but as long as I can get a rough idea\N of the direction and timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.13,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can cut through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:30.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:33.43,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,That was so fast that I wouldn't \Nhave been able to dodge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.51,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:41.23,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Losing a team member is a handicap,\Nbut we won't be able to win at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:46.48,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave Mr. Useless behind and \Nfigure something out ourselves, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:52.88,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pinpoint the enemy's position and hold \Nthem down while you protect the crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:57.00,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Then the two of us can close in on their \Ncrystal and try to destroy it directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.33,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This is our only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.83,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa thought of that so quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:04.33,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She must've survived all kinds of battles, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:09.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is our first joint \Noperation together, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:10.81,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Our first?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:12.93,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.28,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:21.06,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they're actually trying to \Ncharge in with just the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.84,main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:26.49,main,Guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the other member of B Team asleep? \NIs he trying to lower his opponents' guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:31.32,main,Guy 5,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on his abilities, I guess \Nthis could be a way of fighting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.93,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is this actually interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:37.85,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Going on a date with me would've \Nbeen way more fun, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:41.86,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why do you look so uninterested?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:44.97,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to make you smile myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.83,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:51.88,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are doing \Nsurprisingly well out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.68,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not that I care or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.35,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best out there, Mimosa and Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.73,main,Rick,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:04.69,main,Rick,0000,0000,0000,,He's blocking those combo spells so easily \Nand charging at us with their crystal in tow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.69,main,Rick,0000,0000,0000,,They're heading right for our crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:11.29,italics,Rick,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently one of them can \Ndetect positions, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:12.68,italics,Rick,0000,0000,0000,,They've almost reached midrange—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.20,main,Ast,0000,0000,0000,,I see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Two enemies and their crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:18.60,main,Forti,0000,0000,0000,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.93,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:24.35,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Our crystal is unharmed, but their \Ncrystal is already falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.54,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Plant Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.46,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Rock Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.35,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Cannon Flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.17,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Rock Fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:42.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,When'd you learn such an \Nawesome attack spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:49.07,flashbackitalics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... The next time we meet, I'll be \Nstrong enough to fight alongside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.77,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.78,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.68,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:07.91,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.83,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're so damn reliable, Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.97,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,We've only just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.34,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Cannon Flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.02,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:25.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,She's not just cute. She's strong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.49,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That gap is irresistible! \NI wish she'd come my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:31.15,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:34.51,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna fight her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:41.16,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,She's grown as a woman. Maybe it's \Nbecause she's on the same team as Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:45.82,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,To think that she can fight so boldly \Nin front of all those people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.62,top,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you have such a good teammate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:46.62,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:52.82,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'd been admiring your growth \Nas I was working out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.95,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,but I had no idea you'd progressed so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:57.13,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored to be your senior, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.97,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa's working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:03.32,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That means I need to work even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:04.85,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.33,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:10.46,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,You smiled? You just smiled a little, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:13.08,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo! I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:15.36,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't smiling. You just imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.27,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, you're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:21.56,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,But... That's also one of \Nthe reasons I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:22.36,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:26.04,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like she'll mature \Neven more in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:31.99,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! You can do it, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.13,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you nummies when you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:41.66,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,There are two of them. \NShall we move closer and surround them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:46.43,main,Forti,0000,0000,0000,,No. The little gray-haired \Nboy has an anti-magic sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:50.36,main,Forti,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him use it before.\NIt's invincible in close combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.42,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:57.02,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard rumors about it, \Nbut to think a little boy like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:00.24,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably dangerous to get too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.22,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They split up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Which one has the crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:10.91,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Flower Guidepost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.13,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This response...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.35,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:21.92,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-magic child!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.18,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Behold my ultimate spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.02,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What an intense concentration of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.20,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful attack spell is incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:33.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut that, and then the crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:35.71,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.69,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,There are two similar responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:41.61,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,The other two have powerful \Nmidrange attack spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.61,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This position... We're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:49.24,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,If any of those attacks hit \Nthe crystal, we're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.02,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:54.54,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,If they attack simultaneously, even Asta \Nwon't be able to hold them both back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.04,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:03.88,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:07.97,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:10.56,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:21.69,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,One of them can use paralysis trap magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.75,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,When did they...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.99,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to tell what'll happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:32.99,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Royal Knights Selection Exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:40.88,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.01,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,From three directions?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:56.69,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to avoid all three attacks.\NThis... might be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:15.83,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.83,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Our spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.94,italics,All,0000,0000,0000,,They reflected our spells back at us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.66,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What was that magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:46.03,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:55.54,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:06.25,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like that went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:13.30,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:18.95,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,That's a senior Magic Knight for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:22.31,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that would've destroyed \Ntheir crystal, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:28.35,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,But to think he managed to keep the \Ncrystal intact and stay conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:30.36,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:35.78,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Though it looks like you and the \Ncrystal are both on your last legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:40.04,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... I don't know \Nwhat else might happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.98,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,so I need to take the shortest possible \Nroute to destroy that crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:51.88,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,The crystal will never...\Nfall to someone as insolent as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.14,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Says the person who just lost to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.14,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:02.14,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're short on imagination \Nwhen it comes to unknown magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:06.89,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights are supposed to consider \Nevery possibility when fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.31,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,If people could win by getting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:12.91,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,all fired up and launching \Nhuge spells, life would be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:16.99,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who loses to me doesn't \Ndeserve to be a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:21.29,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,That magic is... Ash Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:26.26,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,That means the trap spell \Nthat Asta fell for was his?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.08,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,This is game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:32.34,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You trash can try again some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.27,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.91,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You know, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:44.60,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not here to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.30,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm here for a \Ncompletely different reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.11,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.22,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Psych, you loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:05.32,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Crystal magic stoppage confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.69,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,B Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:18.31,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What was with that guy's magic, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:21.22,main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,He powered up his opponents' spells \Nand reflected them back to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:25.16,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but that was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:29.19,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that weirdo in the mask is the \Ntop candidate for the Royal Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:34.90,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that Asta and his team won, \Nbut I'm really annoyed for some reason, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:39.24,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,And the best cure for that is to eat, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.53,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, great work, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.10,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,That was some nice teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:52.50,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You did a great job as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.98,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that guy's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:58.51,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,For a second, he actually \Nthought I wouldn't destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:02.72,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:10.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You jackass! What the hell \Nis with your attitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:14.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do that to a Magic Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That team was amazing, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:20.07,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing or not, they still lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:24.49,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,It just means our teamwork \Nwas better than theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.20,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Be glad, you shitty little shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Teamwork? You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:33.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That trap I triggered was \Nyour magic, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:35.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:38.84,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Again, I had you fall for the \Ntrap so you could act as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:42.26,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You know what they say... If you want to \Nfool your enemies, fool your friends first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The hell's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:46.39,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. There's a spell \Nset on my collar, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:52.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes! My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:53.70,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes! My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:57.53,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.61,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:04.41,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,He probably seals magic effects in objects \Nor the terrain by drawing magic circles,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:07.45,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,then uses certain conditions \Nto activate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:13.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That trap activated after Asta \Ntriggered the earlier trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:18.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It responded to magic that entered \Nthe area within a certain time frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:23.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It's called... a counter-trap spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.66,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It sends magic back at double \Nthe speed and power,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:30.98,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,so the stronger the spell, \Nthe more effective it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:40.57,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,A huge trap spell like that must have \Ntaken an enormous amount of mana and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:42.78,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,When did you even set it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:46.79,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's still in my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.16,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you sleeping the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:50.06,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret. It's always better \Nwhen a guy's a bit mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mysterious, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:54.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You crazy, cool-masked jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:57.55,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,That's a compliment, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us everything, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:06.85,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're loud, no matter \Nwho you're talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:11.39,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We're on stage next, so clear the hell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:14.22,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Who died and made you the \Nboss, Funglasquent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:16.86,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't abbreviate "Funny Glasses Delinquent!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:20.97,main,MagnA,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell kind of name is that, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:23.29,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You're plenty loud yourself, Funglashorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:27.08,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling "Funny Glasses Shorty," \Nyou ridiculously giant woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:32.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna! Giant Lady! And... where's the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:42.73,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... All of you lack elegance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:44.38,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Geh... Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:52.91,sign_29885_315_C_Team_The_Coral,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(732,1035)}C Team\NThe Coral Peacocks 1st Class Senior Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Kirsch Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:48.34,top,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You're not beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:52.73,top,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best not to taint my beauty, \Nfor I am Kirsch Vermillion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.40,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell's that sparkly guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say Vermillion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.90,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,He's my older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Older brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.47,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he'd disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:07.31,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I am beautiful. Oh, so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He seems like a fun big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:15.62,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I wish from the bottom of \Nmy heart that he'd disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:02.27,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:01.18,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:05.78,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}The Next Time We Meet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:05.00,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,The Next Time We Meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:13.03,flashbackitalics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... The next time we meet, I'll be \Nstrong enough to fight alongside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:16.79,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Black... Clover... Black... Clover...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:16.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:20.79,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Black... Clover... Black... Clover...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.94,0:23:20.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:24.00,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Black... Clover... Black... Clover...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:23.50,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:24.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:28.80,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, I've gotten stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.83,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You can...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:35.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa, when did you learn to \Ndo an awesome serve like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:36.79,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.27,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there. Aren't I beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.74,0:23:44.86,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,The beauty that stands before \Nyou is I, Kirsch Vermillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:47.11,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I am Mimosa's beautiful brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:51.18,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, \NBeautiful Page 75: "Fierce Battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 75\N\N{\fs18} Fierce Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:23:53.15,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sin to be so beautiful.
